'''Arian''' ({{lang-fa|آرین}}) is an [[Iran]]ian newspaper in the [[Fars Province|Fars]] region. The [[Concessionaire]] of this magazine was ''Hosein Partow'' known as Setoodeh and it was published in [[Shiraz]] since 1914.<ref>Rumi,Siroos; List of printed matters of Fars;2006;[[Ministry of Culture and Islamic Guidance (Iran)]]</ref>

